regarding fermat 's use of ascent , weil continued " the novelty consisted in the vastly extended use which fermat made of it , giving him at least a partial equivalent of what we would obtain by the systematic use of the group theoretical properties of the rational points on a standard cubic."weil 1984 , p.105 with his gift for number relations and his ability to find proofs for many of his theorems , fermat essentially created the modern theory of numbers .

